OL,6,FSome home insurance customers could
OL,7,Ffind themselves at risk of claims
OL,8,Fbeing rejected because the wrong kind
OL,9,Fof weather was involved, according to
OL,10,FWhich?
OL,12,FThe consumer group has raised concerns
OL,13,Fthat insurance claims could be turned
OL,14,Fdown by some providers for what it
OL,15,Fconsiders to be potentially unfair
OL,16,Fdefinitions of storms and floods.
