OL,3,CSome insurance claims may risk wrong-
OL,4,Ckind-of-weather rejection ` Which?
OL,6,FThe consumer group looked at 133
OL,7,Finsurance policies sold by 67 firms,
OL,8,Fand said that nearly a third (32%) of
OL,9,Fhome insurance policies contain what
OL,10,Fit views as potentially unfair flood
OL,11,Fdefinitions, and a fifth (20%) of
OL,12,Fpolicies have potentially unfair storm
OL,13,Fdefinitions.
OL,15,FWhich? believes flood definitions
OL,16,Fcould be potentially unfair if they
OL,17,Fexclude gradual, slow and steady entry
OL,18,Fof water into or outside a building,
OL,19,Ffor example by specifying that water
OL,20,Fmust have entered suddenly or rapidly.
